{"id":"concepts/robots-txt","title":"robots.txt","type":"concepts","html":"<h1>robots.txt</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. Web standard file telling crawlers what to index. In the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/ai-visibility-engine\">AI visibility</a> context, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/rankett\">rankett</a> updates client robots.txt + adds an <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/llm-txt\">LLM.txt</a> file as part of week-1 technical setup so AI search engines can discover and recommend the business — see <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-12-30-direct-offer\">2025 12 30 direct offer</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Related</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/llm-txt\">llm txt</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/schema-markup-for-ai\">schema markup for ai</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/ai-visibility-engine\">ai visibility engine</a></li>\n</ul>\n","related":[{"id":"summaries/2025-12-30-direct-offer","label":"2025 12 30 Direct Offer"},{"id":"concepts/ai-visibility-engine","label":"AI Visibility Engine"},{"id":"concepts/llm-txt","label":"LLM.txt"},{"id":"projects/rankett","label":"Rankett"},{"id":"concepts/schema-markup-for-ai","label":"Schema Markup for AI"}]}
